text = "[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#1a202c]

[table=2]
[cell][bgcolor=#00205b][color=#ffffff][b]  Financial Conduct Authority  [/b][/color][/bgcolor][/cell]
[cell][color=#4a6080]  [url=fca-securereport.gov.uk]Home[/url]   About   Guidance   Contact[/color][/cell]
[/table]

[indent]
[bgcolor=#00205b][color=#ffffff]
[font_size=14][b]Secure Reporting Portal[/b][/font_size]
[font_size=11]Report financial crime, market abuse, or regulatory misconduct[/font_size]
[/color][/bgcolor]

─────────────────────────────────────────────────

[color=#1a202c]All reports are handled in strict confidence. You may report anonymously. We do not share your identity with third parties without your explicit consent.

Reports submitted here are reviewed by the FCA's Intelligence Division. Where evidence meets the threshold for investigation, cases are escalated to the Enforcement Division.[/color]

─────────────────────────────────────────────────

[b]Anonymous Report Form[/b]

[bgcolor=#ffffff]
[color=#4a6080]Nature of misconduct[/color]
[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#888888]  Select type...  ▾  [/color][/bgcolor]

[color=#4a6080]Organisation involved[/color]
[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#888888]  Enter company name or registration number  [/color][/bgcolor]

[color=#4a6080]Description of misconduct[/color]
[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#888888]  Describe what you have witnessed or discovered...  [/color][/bgcolor]

[color=#4a6080]Evidence upload[/color] [color=#888888](max 2GB — supports PDF, ZIP, documents)[/color]
[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#1a6bb5]  + Attach file  [/color][/bgcolor]

[color=#4a6080]Contact details[/color] [color=#888888](optional — leave blank to remain anonymous)[/color]
[bgcolor=#f0f4f8][color=#888888]  Email or secure contact  [/color][/bgcolor]

[bgcolor=#00205b][color=#ffffff][b]  [url=fca_submit_check]Submit Report →[/url]  [/b][/color][/bgcolor]

[color=#888888][font_size=11]For your protection, we recommend submitting over Tor if anonymity is required. Submissions from standard connections may include metadata.[/font_size][/color]
[/bgcolor]

─────────────────────────────────────────────────

[color=#4a6080]Not sure if your information is relevant? [url=fca-securereport.gov.uk/guidance][color=#1a6bb5]Read our submission guidance →[/color][/url][/color]

[/indent]

[color=#6a8099][font_size=10]Financial Conduct Authority · 12 Endeavour Square, London E20 1JN · Authorised and regulated · Crown Copyright[/font_size][/color]

[/color][/bgcolor]"